::KitKat::
She smiled at Destructor. "Thank you. I appreciate the use of your 
base.  We may use your base as our permenant home once we are doning 
making sure the old cave is vacant.  Please help Drillbit sweep the 
cave for any other bot activity.  Also, while you are looking around 
inside the cave, if you see anything that might of any use, please 
get it.  We may have need of any useable equipment."
